metadata.name: Noodle #1
metadata.description: Noodle Boy is ready to explore the best food and recipes in the galaxy! With the help of our Noodle friends, we set off on our mission, hungry and eager to eat. You can join Noodle Boy by wrapping your Noodle to build your very own food ship. Space Noodles is comprised of over 80 audio & visual traits. Each Space Noodle also comes with randomly generated on-chain stats and may be utilized in future experiences. Noodspeed!
